What is UNIX?
-----------------
It is an operating system created in 1960s.

How it is relevant till date?
-------------------------------
With lot of extentions and improvements to base version, several flavours introduced by organizations/companies(Redhat Linux,Ubuntu,Suse...)

Characteristics of UNIX :
------------------------------
1.It is freeware.
2.It is Open source software.
It is FOSS(Freeware and Open source software)
3.It is multi user operating system.
4.It is multi tasking operating system.
5.It is user-friendly and supports  both CUI/GUI.
6.It is more secure than windows operating system.

